<h2><span id="Ruy_Lopez_-_Bird.27s_Defence"></span><span id="Ruy_Lopez_-_Bird's_Defence">Ruy Lopez - Bird's Defence</span></h2>
<p>Black gives up the defense of e5 and instead counter-attacks with a threat towards the bishop.  The drawback is that after the knight exchange on d4 Black will have a slightly inferior pawn structure, though with a slight space gain.
</p>
<dl><dd><b>1.e4 e5 2.Nf3 Nc6 3.Bb5 Nd4</b></dd></dl><h2><span id="References">References</span></h2>
